{"sections":[],"metadata":{"title":"set(clearFunc:)","modules":[{"name":"GLib"}],"symbolKind":"method","extendedModule":"GLib","roleHeading":"Instance Method","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"set","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"clearFunc","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"GDestroyNotify","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@GDestroyNotify"},{"kind":"text","text":"?)"}],"externalID":"s:4GLib13ArrayProtocolPAAE3set9clearFuncyySvSgXCSg_tF","role":"symbol"},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/ArrayProtocol\/set(clearFunc:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"set"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"clearFunc"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@GDestroyNotify","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"GDestroyNotify"},{"kind":"text","text":"? = nil)"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"clearFunc"},{"type":"text","text":" will be called when an element in the array"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"data segment is removed and when the array is freed and data","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"segment is deallocated as well. "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"clearFunc"},{"type":"text","text":" will be passed a"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"pointer to the element to clear, rather than the element itself."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note that in contrast with other uses of [callback"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/DestroyNotify","isActive":true},{"text":"]","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"functions, "},{"code":"clearFunc","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is expected to clear the contents of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the array element it is given, but not free the element itself."}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"c","code":["typedef struct","{","  gchar *str;","  GObject *obj;","} ArrayElement;","","static void","array_element_clear (ArrayElement *element)","{","  g_clear_pointer (&element->str, g_free);","  g_clear_object (&element->obj);","}","","\/\/ main code","GArray *garray = g_array_new (FALSE, FALSE, sizeof (ArrayElement));","g_array_set_clear_func (garray, (GDestroyNotify) array_element_clear);","\/\/ assign data to the structure","g_array_free (garray, TRUE);"]}],"kind":"content"}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib","doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/ArrayProtocol"]]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/glib\/arrayprotocol\/set(clearfunc:)"]}],"abstract":[{"text":"Sets a function to clear an element of ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"array"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"references":{"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib/DestroyNotify":{"url":"\/documentation\/glib\/destroynotify","title":"DestroyNotify","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"typealias"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"DestroyNotify"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/DestroyNotify","abstract":[{"text":"Specifies the type of function which is called when a data element","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"is destroyed. It is passed the pointer to the data element and","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"should free any memory and resources allocated for it."}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"DestroyNotify","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib/ArrayProtocol":{"fragments":[{"text":"protocol","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"ArrayProtocol","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"ArrayProtocol","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","title":"ArrayProtocol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Contains the public fields of a "},{"code":"GArray","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/ArrayProtocol","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/glib\/arrayprotocol"},"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib":{"url":"\/documentation\/glib","kind":"symbol","title":"GLib","abstract":[],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib","role":"collection"},"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib/ArrayProtocol/set(clearFunc:)":{"title":"set(clearFunc:)","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets a function to clear an element of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"array"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"url":"\/documentation\/glib\/arrayprotocol\/set(clearfunc:)","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"set"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"clearFunc"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"GDestroyNotify","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@GDestroyNotify"},{"kind":"text","text":"?)"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/ArrayProtocol\/set(clearFunc:)","type":"topic","role":"symbol"}}}